result.name: Guts Soul Kamameshi

reviews.text:
Guts Soul Kamameshi is a newly opened Japanese restaurant in my neighborhood that serves kamameshi. Kamameshi literally translates to “kettle rice” and is a traditional Japanese rice dish cooked in an iron pot called kama.

We ordered this Dirty Deep Fried Banana as dessert. However, it was served before the main. It was amazing though! The dirty part is actually chocolate powder, which is quite sweet. And the fresh hot deep fried banana is so delicious! It’s fluffy and moist instead of crispy. Surprisingly it wasn’t overly sweet. It actually tastes like that monkey banana chocolate, if you know what I mean.

There are 2 stream of unagi kamameshi - gold and silver. And under each stream there are 3 choices, which is from least to most luxurious in terms of texture. My first choice was sold out when I visited at about 8pm, so I opted for this Silver Ungai Kamameshi which is the cheapest one on the menu.

It was dry without the soya sauce for eel. So I had to add it myself. The sauce is available for free in the restaurant, you can ask the shop assistants for that. The rice was soft and round, which was very delicious. Love the burnt rice at the bottom of the kettle too. Eel was good! Meaty and not too oily.

Ordered chicken wings, grilled eel rice and panfried chicken rice. Chicken wings are fine, just not used tot he sweet taste of the deep fried chicken wings. All the rice is too dry not much sauce which make it difficult to chew. Haven't tried any other dishes, but so far not recommended.
Their signature unagi Don is okay, nothing special. However, the quality of rice is poor, service was limited and they use cash as their sole means of payment.
unagi rice with reasonable price
nice, lunch price is good value.

result.name: Amoy Plaza

reviews.text: Old private estate shopping mall struggling to compete with new ones.  It is not the new huge malls with high ceilings big brands but you may like the surprises and the rare shops at the corners or far end of corridors.  There are a few shops selling expert model kits for adults and toys for teenagers and game console games also.
Many good restaurants, many hobby stores. Something for everyone. Best of all, affordable price.
Many delicious food such as Genki Sushi and Pizza Hut

A lot of choices to choose from, a cinema and stuff like that. What you would hope from a decent shopping mall. There are also housing estates above the shopping centre but ofc it's too expensive for a normal human being in Hong Kong to afford
Nice concentrated shops and diversity.

result.name: 釜之魂釜飯專門店

reviews.text:
有驚喜！下午茶230-430，便廿蚊
鰻魚好食丫 係咸左少少姐
飯粒粒分明 口感我鍾意
跟餐有野飲 麵豉湯 泡菜
嗌左柚子蜜都足料喔！
有啲餐廳溝到淡茂茂好鬼難飲架！
天氣成三十幾度，成間鋪頭由椅腳到天花板都出哂倒汗水，依然唔肯去閂門。再加咪個釜飯，簡直入左地獄，熱到完全無胃口食飯。同職員講可唔可以閂左隻門佢，佢話係裝飾來唔閂得，簡直不知所謂。以後都唔會再去

It made feel like a fish out of a water when someone leave you away.
-
食野除左本身食材重要之外.環境同氣氛都好緊要,係九龍灣呢間頗時尚風格既鰻魚飯主題餐廳,裝潢已經吸晴不少!👇
-
📌金魂(厚肉) - $138
👉份量睇落好似唔多,但鰻魚係有驚喜,可能係order左個厚肉,所以肉質相當淋身,修口有融化感覺,汁底做得好好,調味岩岩好,我好鍾意佢既配料,有d南瓜蓉同粟米,底有少少飯焦,岩哂我口味,好食!
-
📌鹽麴牛舌飯 - $98
👉主要牛舌算係幾有咬口,香味亦都合格,
都係一樣有南瓜蓉攪碎撈埋d汁同個飯1齊食真係好和味!食得過!
環境舒適，食物質素勝在平均，不錯，炸豆腐幾好味
環境舒適，鰻魚肥美，汁好味，喜歡吃飯焦的人一定很喜歡，這是餐廳的特色。牛肉食美味，朱古力炸香蕉一般。可以再來。
